				<td colspan="2"><span>Hey all.  After a long stretch, I made a rough draft of the bard issues list.  I need help to finish it, though.  Please visit the link below, take a look at the issues, and add any corrections or contributions you can think of.  We're not discussing the relative merits of each issue at this point, but rather just trying to define and research them properly.  Once we have every issue clearly defined, then we'll move on to discussing priorities.
<br />

