				<td colspan="2"><span>I have a point to add, if you happen to see it, Feroce:
<br />

<br />
Fix that blasted bug that has been around since the beginning:
<br />

<br />
You feel divinely inspired.
<br />
Your inspiration fades.
<br />
You feel divinely inspired.
<br />

<br />
Song poofs from your short buff box.
<br />

<br />
The bug we love to hate, the &quot;I refreshed my song at the exact moment it was set to fade and server/client delays caused it to fade anyway.&quot;  This can happen with any spell, but bard songs see it a lot more often because they're refreshed frequently.
<br />

<br />
True, when it happens to us it usually doesn't happen to our groupmates due to tick timer differences, but it's still extremely annoying, especially if the song in question is...say...Psalm of Veeshan versus Uber_Nuker_Mob93.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
